&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Upbound is redefining how modern infrastructure is built for the Agentic AI Era. We’re the creators and primary maintainers of&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Crossplane&lt;/strong&gt;, and we’re building the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Intelligent Control Plane&lt;/strong&gt;—a new platform layer that makes infrastructure&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;programmable, autonomous, and composable&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
