&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As Director of Control Planes &amp;amp; Ecosystem&lt;/strong&gt;, you will own the strategy and execution for the customer-facing control plane experience across:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Crossplane:&lt;/strong&gt; Upstream work and contributions for the open source Crossplane Project&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Upbound Crossplane:&lt;/strong&gt; Upbound’s Enterprise Distribution of Crossplane&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Upbound Marketplace: &lt;/strong&gt;The place where Users and Customers discover content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Upbound Official Providers and Extensions:&lt;/strong&gt; Development and maintenance of Providers, Add-Ons, Functions, and more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partner Integrations: &lt;/strong&gt;Development of Extensions with third party partners&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
